{"word":"H7153 - קִרְיַת אַרְבַּע - Qiryath ʼArbaʻ - keer-yath' ar-bah' - Kirjath-arba","slug":"H7153","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קִרְיַת אַרְבַּע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Qiryath ʼArbaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>keer-yath' ar-bah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Kirjath-arba"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05E8;&#x05D9;&#x05EA; &#x05D4;&#x05D0;&#x05E8;&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05E2;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E7;&#x05E8;&#x05D9;&#x05EA; &#x05D0;&#x05E8;&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05E2; - qiryath 'arba&#x201B;  qiryath ha&#x0302;'arba&#x201B;</b> - <i>(keer-yath') ar-bah', haw-ar-bah'</i><p/>The second form, used in <a href='B:160 11:25'>Neh 11:25</a>, has the article interposed; from <a href=\"#/H7151\">H7151</a> and <a href=\"#/H704\">H704</a> or <a href=\"#/H702\">H702</a>; <i>city of Arba</i>, or <i>city of the four</i> (giants); <i>Kirjath-Arba</i> or <i>Kirjath-ha-Arba</i>, a place in Palestine: - Kirjath-arba."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4745\">H4745</a>, <a href=\"#/H4746\">H4746</a>, <a href=\"#/H6982\">H6982</a>, <a href=\"#/H704\">H704</a>, <a href=\"#/H7136\">H7136</a>, <a href=\"#/H7137\">H7137</a>, <a href=\"#/H7147\">H7147</a>, <a href=\"#/H7151\">H7151</a>, <a href=\"#/H7152\">H7152</a>, <a href=\"#/H7154\">H7154</a>, <a href=\"#/H7155\">H7155</a>, <a href=\"#/H7156\">H7156</a>, <a href=\"#/H7157\">H7157</a>, <a href=\"#/H7158\">H7158</a>, <a href=\"#/H7176\">H7176</a>, <a href=\"#/H7177\">H7177</a>, <a href=\"#/H7178\">H7178</a>"}]}